/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾廿年前無端端有條扈佬行入去屋村,傻既都知咩事啦</blockquote><br />\n最緊要係官員唔知, 冇得粉飾太平<br />\n知佢係港督, 反映民意有咩問題??</blockquote><br />\n你睇下, d貨擺得幾齊,幾靚, 冇放出界<br />\n一定有人事先通水</blockquote><br />\n睇下內文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麥理浩知下邊洗太平地之後就自己帶副官出 無通知其他人"},{"pid":"f0f31824883fbaf25e9ca88e338d21320739e4f6","tid":89414,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"麥Sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5d1f811c8982b72f59c0b8cf6334398cc55205","tid":89414,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaPNA8YSx2a5qu7eCi67AKdq4PkTEqCBbF4bvkKWYiagk?filename=591731v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F591731v.png&h=d9d62091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回個靚帶"},{"pid":"3fce2b993e09cd3cfe2ae602f54a69f5bb285e7e","tid":89414,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaPNA8YSx2a5qu7eCi67AKdq4PkTEqCBbF4bvkKWYiagk?filename=591731v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F591731v.png&h=d9d62091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回個靚帶</blockquote><br />\n習近平幾年前有習八條<br />\n講搞活動要盡量少排場<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦、張德江、CY等人明顯係同習近平搞對抗"},{"pid":"6fdd5a7abebe83b60de61c146a4b274643757aa1","tid":89414,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"Each house estate should be better than the last one.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86578834f2b305a2434b426d75b8ce8a3a5237f4","tid":89414,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2